---
// Hero.astro — Full-viewport hero, impact-first messaging, differentiated from competition
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden circuit-bg"
  aria-label="Hero section"
>
  <!-- ── Circuit / Grid Overlay ── -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 circuit-dots opacity-40 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <!-- ── SVG Circuit Pattern (decorative) ── -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg
      class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-full h-full opacity-10"
      viewBox="0 0 1200 800"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice"
    >
      <path d="M800 0 L800 200 L1000 200 L1000 400 L1200 400" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="8 4"/>
      <path d="M900 0 L900 100 L1100 100 L1100 300 L1200 300" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/>
      <path d="M1000 0 L1000 50 L1200 50" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="4 6"/>
      <path d="M0 200 L200 200 L200 400 L400 400" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/>
      <path d="M0 500 L300 500 L300 700 L600 700" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="8 4"/>
      <path d="M200 800 L200 600 L400 600 L400 400" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="5 5"/>
      <circle cx="800" cy="200" r="5" fill="#B97333" opacity="0.6"/>
      <circle cx="1000" cy="200" r="5" fill="#B97333" opacity="0.6"/>
      <circle cx="1000" cy="400" r="5" fill="#B97333" opacity="0.6"/>
      <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="4" fill="#B97333" opacity="0.5"/>
      <circle cx="400" cy="400" r="5" fill="#B97333" opacity="0.6"/>
      <circle cx="300" cy="500" r="5" fill="#B97333" opacity="0.6"/>
      <circle cx="900" cy="650" r="200" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1" fill="none" opacity="0.2"/>
      <circle cx="900" cy="650" r="140" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="0.5" fill="none" opacity="0.15"/>
      <path d="M820 600 Q900 520 980 600 Q900 680 820 600Z" stroke="#B97333" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.3"/>
    </svg>
    <!-- Floating particles -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-copper opacity-40" style="animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-copper opacity-30" style="animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite 1s;"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/3 left-1/3 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-copper opacity-20" style="animation: float 7s ease-in-out infinite 2s;"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-2/3 right-1/3 w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-copper opacity-35" style="animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite 3s;"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Radial gradient overlay ── -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 70% at 50% 50%, rgba(11,27,50,0.2) 0%, rgba(11,27,50,0.7) 100%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- ── Hero Content ── -->
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center pt-24">

    <!-- Main Headline — Claim principal según Manual de Marca -->
    <h1
      class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-3"
      style="letter-spacing: -0.03em; animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease 0.25s forwards; opacity: 0;"
    >
      <span data-i18n="hero.title">Minería Urbana<br/>de Precisión</span>
    </h1>
    <!-- Segundo claim de marca -->
    <p
      class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold mb-6"
      style="color: #B97333; animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease 0.35s forwards; opacity: 0;"
      data-i18n="hero.claim2"
    >Recursos Infinitos</p>

    <!-- Subtitle — strategic partner angle, not compliance language -->
    <p
      class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 leading-relaxed"
      style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease 0.4s forwards; opacity: 0;"
      data-i18n="hero.subtitle"
    >
      No somos solo un gestor de retiro. Somos tu socio estratégico para
      convertir residuos electrónicos en activos medibles y cumplimiento REP sin fricción.
    </p>

    <!-- Differentiator line — what no competitor says -->
    <p
      class="text-sm max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10"
      style="color: rgba(185,115,51,0.85); animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease 0.55s forwards; opacity: 0;"
      data-i18n="hero.differentiator"
    >
      El único gestor en Chile que te muestra cada paso, desde el retiro hasta el material recuperado.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Buttons -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center mb-14"
      style="animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease 0.65s forwards; opacity: 0;"
    >
      <!-- Primary CTA: frictionless scheduling -->
      <a
        href="#contacto"
        class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-4 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl"
        style="background-color: #B97333; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(185,115,51,0.35);"
        data-i18n="hero.cta2"
      >
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
        </svg>
        Agenda tu retiro ahora
      </a>

      <!-- Secondary CTA -->
      <a
        href="#cadena"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-4 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold text-white border-2 border-white/25 hover:border-copper hover:bg-white/8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
        data-i18n="hero.cta1"
      >
        Ver cómo funciona
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- ── Bouncing scroll indicator ── -->
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2"
    aria-hidden="true"
    style="animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease 1.3s forwards; opacity: 0;"
  >
    <span class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">Scroll</span>
    <div class="bounce-arrow">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="color: rgba(185,115,51,0.7);">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
    50%       { transform: translateY(-12px) rotate(3deg); }
  }
</style>
